column5: Fits well and colour looks good. Handwashed it once and colour has not faded. Stitching isn't so great. The pockets peep out from the inside if you haven't zipped up, which looks weird. Not thick enough material for winter wear. Works great for a cool day/night of around 20 degrees C.
